headline: MasterCard price target raised to $565 from $550 at BMO Capital
summary: BMO Capital analyst Rufus Hone raised the firm’s price target on MasterCard (MA) to $565 from $550 and keeps an Outperform rating on the shares. The company has outlined 2025-2027 financial targets and addressed investor concerns around the remaining runway in consumer payments and Mastercard’s ability to accelerate secular shift in commercial payments/new flows, the analyst tells investors in a research note.
